<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>“冬之恋”系列音乐会之二</strong><strong> </strong></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: large;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2012</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">12</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1</span>日晚19:30<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">              </span>地点：中央民族乐团民族音乐厅</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: large;">主持人：王军<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">（ </span>国家一级演员）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"> </span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">一、合奏《喜临门》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                          </span>刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                </span>《赶花会》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                          </span>刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">二、二胡独奏《山村小景》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                              </span>陈耀星曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                        </span>《战马奔腾》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                              </span>陈耀星曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                            演奏：李福华（国家一级演员）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">三、笛子独奏《牧民新歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                              </span>简广易曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                              演奏：马芸（文华奖获奖者）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">四、琵琶独奏《十面埋伏》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                      </span>古曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                        </span>《送你一支玫瑰花》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                          </span>新疆民歌改编</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                           演奏：尹萩薇</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">五、古筝独奏《乡韵》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                      </span>周煜国曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                           演奏：王雅雯</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">六、京胡与乐队《柳青娘》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                  </span>吴华曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                           京胡演奏：张学琴<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">          </span>司鼓：李文博</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">七、丝弦五重奏《天山之春》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                      </span>胡登跳编曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                          演奏：肖珺华等</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">八、唢呐独奏《百鸟争鸣》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                      </span>山东民间乐曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                           演奏：陈力宝</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">九、女声独唱《又唱浏阳河》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                       </span>郭天柱词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">   </span>邓东源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                        《黑缎子坎肩》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                  </span>鄂尔多斯民歌</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                           </span>演唱：郭娅丽</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十、板胡独奏《风雪中的爬犁》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                      </span>刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                演奏：刘湘（国家一级演员）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十一、合奏《洗衣歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                               </span>西藏民歌<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">   </span>刘明源编曲</span></span></p>
